lead_paragraph: Caroline Wozniacki overcame injury to beat Japanese teenager Naomi Osaka 7-5, 6-3 and win the Pan Pacific Open on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Wozniacki Beats Japanese Teen Osaka to Win Pan Pacific Open
